<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>战区</title><link>https://www.twz.com</link><description>防御世界的强大进攻。</description><lastBuildDate>Thu, 12 Mar 2026 13:00:18 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>B-2 轰炸机是否刚刚在另一个伊朗核基地投放了 GBU-57 大型穿甲弹？</title><link>https://www.twz.com/air/did-b-2s-just-drop-gbu-57-massive-ordnance-penetrators-on-another-iranian-nuclear-site</link><description>&lt;p&gt;卫星图像显示，伊朗帕尔钦军事基地有一座珍贵的加固设施，顶部整齐排列着三个巨大的撞击点。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;帖子&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com/air/did-b-2s-just-drop-gbu-57-massive-ordnance-penetrators-on-another-iranian-nuclear-site"&gt;B-2 是否刚刚在另一个伊朗核设施上投放了 GBU-57 大型穿甲弹？&lt;/a&gt;首先出现在&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com"&gt;战区&lt;/a&gt;。&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 12 Mar 2026 00:13:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.twz.com/air/did-b-2s-just-drop-gbu-57-massive-ordnance-penetrators-on-another-iranian-nuclear-site</guid></item><item><title>伊朗在霍尔木兹海峡周围升温（更新）</title><link>https://www.twz.com/news-features/iran-turns-up-the-heat-around-the-strait-of-hormuz</link><description>&lt;p&gt;伊朗今天袭击了三艘商船，继续对美国及其盟国造成经济痛苦和政治压力。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com/news-features/iran-turns-up-the-heat-around-the-strait-of-hormuz"&gt;伊朗在霍尔木兹海峡周围升温的帖子（更新）&lt;/a&gt;首先出现在&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com"&gt;战区&lt;/a&gt;。&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 11 Mar 2026 21:44:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.twz.com/news-features/iran-turns-up-the-heat-around-the-strait-of-hormuz</guid></item><item><title>英国加强海外防御姿态以应对伊朗冲突</title><link>https://www.twz.com/uncategorized/uks-grows-its-defensive-posture-abroad-in-response-to-iran-conflict</link><description>&lt;p&gt;英国武装部队加强了在该地区的防空存在，但其战备状态也存在缺陷。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; &lt;a href="https://www.twz.com/uncategorized/uks-grows-its-defensive-posture-abroad-in-response-to-iran-conflict"&gt;英国加强海外防御姿态以应对伊朗冲突&lt;/a&gt;一文首先出现在&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com"&gt;《战区》&lt;/a&gt;上。&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 11 Mar 2026 21:15:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.twz.com/uncategorized/uks-grows-its-defensive-posture-abroad-in-response-to-iran-conflict</guid></item><item><title>B-1B 在英国装载地堡破坏者，这是增强伊朗制空权的迹象</title><link>https://www.twz.com/air/bombers-in-england-being-loaded-with-bunker-busters-a-sign-of-increasing-air-supremacy-over-iran</link><description>&lt;p&gt;目前有 15 架美国轰炸机从英国皇家空军费尔福德基地执行针对伊朗的打击任务。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; &lt;a href="https://www.twz.com/air/bombers-in-england-being-loaded-with-bunker-busters-a-sign-of-increasing-air-supremacy-over-iran"&gt;B-1B 在英国装载地堡破坏者后，伊朗上空的制空权增强的迹象&lt;/a&gt;首先出现在&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com"&gt;战区&lt;/a&gt;。&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 11 Mar 2026 21:08:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.twz.com/air/bombers-in-england-being-loaded-with-bunker-busters-a-sign-of-increasing-air-supremacy-over-iran</guid></item><item><title>伊朗 F-14 雄猫在以色列空袭中遭遇灭亡</title><link>https://www.twz.com/air/iranian-f-14-tomcats-meet-their-doom-in-israeli-airstrikes</link><description>&lt;p&gt;随着美国和以色列寻求削弱伊朗空军，伊朗的“雄猫”战斗机可能已经耗尽了其九架飞机的最后生命。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com/air/iranian-f-14-tomcats-meet-their-doom-in-israeli-airstrikes"&gt;伊朗 F-14 雄猫在以色列空袭中遭遇厄运&lt;/a&gt;后，首先出现在&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com"&gt;战区&lt;/a&gt;。&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 11 Mar 2026 16:50:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.twz.com/air/iranian-f-14-tomcats-meet-their-doom-in-israeli-airstrikes</guid></item><item><title>B-21袭击者首次拍摄空中加油照片</title><link>https://www.twz.com/air/b-21-raider-photographed-aerial-refueling-for-the-first-time</link><description>&lt;p&gt;据称，随着美国空军在 2027 年投入使用之前加速生产，B-21 的测试进展很快。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; &lt;a href="https://www.twz.com/air/b-21-raider-photographed-aerial-refueling-for-the-first-time"&gt;B-21 袭击者首次拍摄到空中加油的&lt;/a&gt;照片首先出现在&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com"&gt;《战区》&lt;/a&gt;上。&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 11 Mar 2026 05:17:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.twz.com/air/b-21-raider-photographed-aerial-refueling-for-the-first-time</guid></item><item><title>史诗般的愤怒第11天：美国承诺对伊朗进行“最猛烈的打击”</title><link>https://www.twz.com/news-features/epic-fury-day-11-u-s-promises-most-intense-day-of-strikes-on-iran</link><description>&lt;p&gt;随着伊朗无人机和导弹继续飞行，美国增加了部署在英国的轰炸机部队。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; &lt;a href="https://www.twz.com/news-features/epic-fury-day-11-u-s-promises-most-intense-day-of-strikes-on-iran"&gt;史诗般的愤怒第 11 天：美国承诺对伊朗进行“最猛烈的打击”&lt;/a&gt;一文首先出现在&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com"&gt;《战区》&lt;/a&gt;上。&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 10 Mar 2026 23:09:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.twz.com/news-features/epic-fury-day-11-u-s-promises-most-intense-day-of-strikes-on-iran</guid></item><item><title>塞尔维亚MiG-29似乎配备了中国超音速防区外导弹</title><link>https://www.twz.com/air/serbian-mig-29-fighter-appears-armed-with-chinese-supersonic-standoff-missiles</link><description>&lt;p&gt;中国制造的 CM-400 空对地导弹以前只在巴基斯坦服役，现在已经出现在塞尔维亚 MiG-29 喷气式飞机上。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;后&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com/air/serbian-mig-29-fighter-appears-armed-with-chinese-supersonic-standoff-missiles"&gt;塞尔维亚 MiG-29 似乎配备了中国超音速防区外导弹&lt;/a&gt;首先出现在&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com"&gt;战区&lt;/a&gt;。&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 10 Mar 2026 22:51:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.twz.com/air/serbian-mig-29-fighter-appears-armed-with-chinese-supersonic-standoff-missiles</guid></item><item><title>发现前往波斯湾的伊朗无人机的能力取得巨大飞跃</title><link>https://www.twz.com/air/massive-leap-in-ability-to-spot-iranian-drones-headed-to-persian-gulf</link><description>&lt;p&gt;E-7A 楔尾飞机可以说是世界上发现低空飞行的伊朗无人机和巡航导弹的最佳飞机。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; &lt;a href="https://www.twz.com/air/massive-leap-in-ability-to-spot-iranian-drones-headed-to-persian-gulf"&gt;发现前往波斯湾的伊朗无人机能力的巨大飞跃&lt;/a&gt;首先出现在&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com"&gt;战区&lt;/a&gt;。&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 10 Mar 2026 22:35:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.twz.com/air/massive-leap-in-ability-to-spot-iranian-drones-headed-to-persian-gulf</guid></item><item><title>美国用弹道导弹袭击伊朗海军舰艇</title><link>https://www.twz.com/land/u-s-striking-iranian-navy-ships-with-ballistic-missiles</link><description>&lt;p&gt;使用弹道导弹远距离打击敌方舰艇是美军未来发展的预演。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com/land/u-s-striking-iranian-navy-ships-with-ballistic-missiles"&gt;美国用弹道导弹袭击伊朗海军舰艇的&lt;/a&gt;帖子首先出现在&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com"&gt;战区&lt;/a&gt;。&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 10 Mar 2026 16:19:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.twz.com/land/u-s-striking-iranian-navy-ships-with-ballistic-missiles</guid></item></channel></rss>